' SD-02. UC-002 전방 장애물 감지 후 정지
' Related Use Case: UC-002. 전방 장애물 감지 후 정지
' Intent: 전방 장애물 감지 시 정지 명령을 생성하고 회피 방향 판단으로 넘기는 흐름을 표현한다.
' Note: 삼면 장애물은 UC-005로, 정지 중 먼지 감지는 UC-006 출력 처리로 이어진다.

@startuml SD_02_UC002_Stop_On_Front_Obstacle
title SD-02 - UC-002 전방 장애물 감지 후 정지

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "MovementCommand" as MovementCommand
participant "AvoidanceDecision" as AvoidanceDecision
actor "주행 장치" as Drive

Sensor -> Controller: reportFrontObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=true)
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: updateFrontObstacle(frontObstacleDetected=true)
Controller -> Cleaning: handleSensorState(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: isFrontObstacleDetected()
SensorState --> Cleaning: true
Cleaning -> Cleaning: changeMovementStatus(AVOIDING_OBSTACLE)
Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(STOP)
MovementCommand --> Cleaning: stopCommand
Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: prepareDirectionDecision()
AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: directionDecisionRequired
Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(stopCommand)
deactivate Cleaning

Controller -> Drive: stop()

alt 전방, 좌측, 우측 장애물이 모두 감지됨
    Sensor -> Controller: reportObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected=true, rightObstacleDetected=true)
    Controller -> SensorState: updateObstacles(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected=true, rightObstacleDetected=true)
    Controller -> Cleaning: handleThreeSideObstacle(SensorState)
    note right of Cleaning: UC-005로 전환
else 정지 중 먼지 감지
    Sensor -> Controller: reportDustDetected()
    Controller -> SensorState: updateDustDetected(dustDetected=true)
    Controller -> Cleaning: markDustResponsePending()
    note right of Cleaning: 주행 회피 판단을 우선하고 청소 출력은 UC-006에 따라 처리
end

deactivate Controller
@enduml
